# Crust local environment overrides.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in values you don't want committed.
# `.env*` is gitignored (this `.env.example` template is the only exception),
# so secrets stay on your machine. Vite inlines these at build/dev time, so
# setting them during `pnpm build` will bake the value into the production
# bundle — keep them out of CI unless you mean it.
#
# Any valid VITE_GIF_* value overrides the matching field in
# public/config.json. Unset, empty, or otherwise invalid values are ignored
# (e.g. VITE_GIF_PROVIDER=tenor falls back to config.json since "tenor" is
# not in the allowlist).

# VITE_GIF_ENABLED=true
# VITE_GIF_PROVIDER=giphy
# VITE_GIF_API_KEY=your-dev-api-key-here
# VITE_GIF_TRENDING_ON_OPEN=true
# VITE_GIF_MAX_RATING=g
